{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "dialogueType": "companion",
  "_comment": "Plan 2 T17 — Junior Officer archetype dialog. Three archetypes: cocky, serious, political. Peer-level tone (officer to officer, not NCO to recruit). Loaded by CompanionDialogueCatalog.",
  "nodes": [

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_intro_greeting",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_greeting_cocky",
      "text": "So you're the other officer the lord's been bragging about. Hope you can keep up — I plan on collecting a banneretcy out of this contract.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "cocky", "is_introduced": false },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "intro_match",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_opt_match_cocky",
          "text": "Then we'll race for it.",
          "tooltip": "Match the swagger (+2 relationship)",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack",
          "action": "rep_change",
          "action_data": { "delta": 2 }
        },
        {
          "id": "intro_dry",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_opt_dry_cocky",
          "text": "Try not to ride your horse off a cliff first.",
          "tooltip": "Tease back (no change)",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack",
          "action": "rep_change",
          "action_data": { "delta": 0 }
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_intro_greeting",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_greeting_serious",
      "text": "We haven't been introduced. The lord speaks well of you — I look forward to working alongside.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "serious", "is_introduced": false },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "intro_warm",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_opt_warm_serious",
          "text": "Likewise. We'll do good work together.",
          "tooltip": "Match the earnestness (+2 relationship)",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack",
          "action": "rep_change",
          "action_data": { "delta": 2 }
        },
        {
          "id": "intro_neutral",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_opt_neutral_serious",
          "text": "Let's see how the first muster goes before we get sentimental.",
          "tooltip": "Stay reserved (no change)",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack",
          "action": "rep_change",
          "action_data": { "delta": 0 }
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_intro_greeting",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_greeting_political",
      "text": "Ah — the new officer. I've been curious. Let's find a moment to compare notes; the lord's circle is more interesting than it looks from the outside.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "political", "is_introduced": false },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "intro_curious",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_opt_curious_political",
          "text": "I'd like that. Plenty I don't know yet.",
          "tooltip": "Show interest (+2 relationship)",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack",
          "action": "rep_change",
          "action_data": { "delta": 2 }
        },
        {
          "id": "intro_cool",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_opt_cool_political",
          "text": "Let's keep our notes professional, shall we?",
          "tooltip": "Hold them at arm's length (-1 relationship)",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack",
          "action": "rep_change",
          "action_data": { "delta": -1 }
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack_cocky",
      "text": "Good. I like an officer with some teeth. Find me when you've got something worth saying.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "cocky" },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "intro_ack_close",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack_opt_close_cocky",
          "text": "Until then.",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack_serious",
      "text": "Understood. The chain of command is what holds this company together — let's make sure we hold up our part of it.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "serious" },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "intro_ack_close",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack_opt_close_serious",
          "text": "Agreed.",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack_political",
      "text": "Excellent. A friendly word at the right ear travels further than a dozen drilled charges. Remember that.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "political" },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "intro_ack_close",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_intro_ack_opt_close_political",
          "text": "I'll remember.",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_root",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_root_default",
      "text": "Got something to discuss, or just stretching your legs?",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer" },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "root_tactical",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_root_opt_tactical",
          "text": "What's your read on our posture?",
          "tooltip": "Peer tactical assessment",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_topic_tactical"
        },
        {
          "id": "root_ambition",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_root_opt_ambition",
          "text": "What are you hoping to get out of this commission?",
          "tooltip": "Ask about their ambitions",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_topic_ambition"
        },
        {
          "id": "root_battle",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_root_opt_battle",
          "text": "Your view on the last engagement?",
          "tooltip": "Recent battle from a peer's view",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_topic_battle",
          "requirements": { "has_recent_battle": true }
        },
        {
          "id": "root_gossip",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_root_opt_gossip",
          "text": "What do you make of the rest of the lord's officers?",
          "tooltip": "Discreet gossip on the lord's circle",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_topic_gossip"
        },
        {
          "id": "root_leave",
          "textId": "companion_junior_officer_root_opt_leave",
          "text": "Carry on.",
          "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_goodbye"
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_topic_tactical",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_tactical_cocky",
      "text": "Posture? We're posturing too cautiously. Give me half a wing of cavalry and I'd already be flanking. The lord's playing the long game when the short game would do.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "cocky" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "tactical_close", "textId": "companion_junior_officer_tactical_opt_close_cocky", "text": "Bold.", "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_topic_tactical",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_tactical_serious",
      "text": "Our line's solid. The flanks need a second cavalry screen if we're committing to open ground — I've been meaning to raise it at the next council. You should second me.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "serious" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "tactical_close", "textId": "companion_junior_officer_tactical_opt_close_serious", "text": "I'll back you on it.", "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_topic_tactical",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_tactical_political",
      "text": "Tactically? Adequate. Politically? The lord's choosing engagements that look impressive in a court report — not the ones that win the campaign. Watch where the dispatches go after each fight.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "political" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "tactical_close", "textId": "companion_junior_officer_tactical_opt_close_political", "text": "Interesting.", "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_topic_ambition",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_ambition_cocky",
      "text": "A banneret's title and a fief I can hunt on. Maybe a song or two with my name in it. I didn't take this commission for the modest pay, that's certain.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "cocky" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "ambition_close", "textId": "companion_junior_officer_ambition_opt_close_cocky", "text": "Aim high.", "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_topic_ambition",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_ambition_serious",
      "text": "A captaincy of my own, in time. Not for the title — for the responsibility. My father served thirty years and never commanded; I owe him the rank he never reached.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "serious" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "ambition_close", "textId": "companion_junior_officer_ambition_opt_close_serious", "text": "Honourable goal.", "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_topic_ambition",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_ambition_political",
      "text": "A seat at the right table. Titles come and go — proximity to the people who decide where titles fall is what lasts. This commission is one rung. There are several more.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "political" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "ambition_close", "textId": "companion_junior_officer_ambition_opt_close_political", "text": "Patient strategy.", "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_topic_battle",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_battle_cocky",
      "text": "Did you see me take that flag? Tell me you saw it. Best charge of the season — I'll be hearing about it for weeks, and I intend to enjoy every word.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "cocky", "has_recent_battle": true },
      "options": [
        { "id": "battle_close", "textId": "companion_junior_officer_battle_opt_close_cocky", "text": "I saw it.", "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_topic_battle",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_battle_serious",
      "text": "We won, but our second line broke later than it should have re-formed. I want to walk the field with you tomorrow and see what we can learn before the next engagement.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "serious", "has_recent_battle": true },
      "options": [
        { "id": "battle_close", "textId": "companion_junior_officer_battle_opt_close_serious", "text": "I'll be there.", "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_topic_battle",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_battle_political",
      "text": "A tidy victory. More importantly, the lord's rivals were watching. Whatever the dispatches say in a week, the real verdict is being whispered tonight in three different camps.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "political", "has_recent_battle": true },
      "options": [
        { "id": "battle_close", "textId": "companion_junior_officer_battle_opt_close_political", "text": "I'll keep an ear out.", "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_topic_gossip",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_gossip_cocky",
      "text": "The senior captain rides like he's afraid of his own horse. The QM hoards saddle-oil. And honestly, you're more competition than the rest of them combined — keep up, would you?",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "cocky" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "gossip_close", "textId": "companion_junior_officer_gossip_opt_close_cocky", "text": "Noted.", "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_topic_gossip",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_gossip_serious",
      "text": "I won't gossip. But I'll say this: two of the captains are due for promotion within the year, and one of them deserves it. The other should not be commanding anything larger than a baggage cart.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "serious" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "gossip_close", "textId": "companion_junior_officer_gossip_opt_close_serious", "text": "Understood.", "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_topic_gossip",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_gossip_political",
      "text": "The senior captain is on his way out — his family's faction lost a key marriage last winter. The chaplain's brother just bought land near the lord's keep. Read the room accordingly.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer", "archetype": "political" },
      "options": [
        { "id": "gossip_close", "textId": "companion_junior_officer_gossip_opt_close_political", "text": "Useful.", "next_node": "companion_junior_officer_root" }
      ]
    },

    {
      "id": "companion_junior_officer_goodbye",
      "speaker": "companion",
      "textId": "companion_junior_officer_goodbye_default",
      "text": "Mind your flank, captain. I'll do the same.",
      "context": { "companion_type": "junior_officer" },
      "options": []
    }
  ]
}
